---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { company } from '../data/site';
---

<Base title={`Terms of Service - ${company.name}`} description="The terms that apply to this website and to engagements with Allaia Studio." path="/terms">
  <Header solid />
  <main id="main" class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pb-24 pt-40 sm:px-8 lg:pt-48">
    <p class="label text-clay-500">Legal</p>
    <h1 class="display mt-5 text-[clamp(2.4rem,6vw,4rem)] text-ink-900">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-base leading-relaxed text-ink-700 [&_h2]:display [&_h2]:mt-12 [&_h2]:text-2xl [&_h2]:text-ink-900 [&_a]:font-semibold [&_a]:text-clay-500 [&_a]:underline">
      <p>
        These terms govern your use of this website. They are not the agreement for our services - paid engagements are
        governed by the separate signed agreement between you and {company.name}.
      </p>

      <h2>Website content</h2>
      <p>
        Information on this site describes our services in general terms and is provided for information only. It is
        not an offer, a quotation, or a guarantee of any particular commercial result. Advertising performance depends
        on factors including your market, offer, budget and operations, and past campaign performance does not
        guarantee future results.
      </p>

      <h2>Engagements</h2>
      <p>
        Scope, fees, contract length and deliverables are set out in your signed agreement. Our standard engagements
        run for a minimum term to allow proper testing and optimisation. Where this site describes plan inclusions,
        those descriptions are indicative and the signed agreement prevails in the event of any inconsistency.
      </p>

      <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>
        The Allaia Studio name, logo, site design and content are our property or used with permission, and may not be
        reproduced without written consent. Ownership of campaign deliverables is addressed in your agreement.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-party platforms</h2>
      <p>
        Our services depend on third-party advertising and messaging platforms. We are not responsible for their
        outages, policy changes, account decisions or pricing changes, though we will work with you to respond to them.
      </p>

      <h2>Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by Philippine law, we are not liable for indirect or consequential loss arising
        from use of this website. Nothing here limits liability that cannot lawfully be limited.
      </p>

      <h2>Governing law</h2>
      <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the Republic of the Philippines.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms: <a href={`mailto:${company.email}`}>{company.email}</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
